      "start": 382.747,
      "end": 385.572,
      "text": "第四，短时间申请好几张卡",
      "slide_index": 10
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start": 385.872,
      "end": 388.512,
      "text": "每一次申请银行都会查你的信用，",
      "slide_index": 10
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start": 388.812,
      "end": 390.548,
      "text": "叫硬查询，会扣分",
      "slide_index": 10
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start": 390.848,
      "end": 393.806,
      "text": "先办一张，用半年再考虑第二张",
      "slide_index": 10
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start": 394.106,
      "end": 396.55,
      "text": "第五，境外刷卡不注意汇率",
      "slide_index": 10
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start": 396.85,
      "end": 401.528,
      "text": "大部分信用卡境外消费会收2.5%的货币转换费",
      "slide_index": 10
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start": 401.828,
      "end": 404.16,
      "text": "刷1000块多付25块，",
      "slide_index": 10
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start": 404.46,
      "end": 406.53,
      "text": "出国前一定要了解清楚",
      "slide_index": 10
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start": 407.33,
      "end": 410.724,
      "text": "总结一下，newcomer办信用卡，一张就够了",
      "slide_index": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start": 411.024,
      "end": 413.757,
      "text": "第一步，问自己逛不逛Costco",
      "slide_index": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start": 414.057,
      "end": 418.413,
      "text": "逛Costco的，直接办CIBC的Costco联名卡，",
      "slide_index": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start": 418.713,
      "end": 420.674,
      "text": "日常消费基本全覆盖",
      "slide_index": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start": 420.974,
      "end": 424.02,
      "text": "又逛Costco又在外面超市买菜的，",
      "slide_index": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start": 424.32,
      "end": 428.025,
      "text": "加一张BMO免费卡，外面超市3%",
      "slide_index": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start": 428.325,
      "end": 431.853,
      "text": "不逛Costco的，首选BMO的CashBack卡",
      "slide_index": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start": 432.153,
      "end": 435.677,
      "text": "BMO办不了的，试其他四大行免费卡，",
      "slide_index": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start": 435.977,
      "end": 438.137,
      "text": "都被拒了走secured路线",
      "slide_index": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start": 438.437,
      "end": 442.293,
      "text": "先建好信用记录，等收入稳定再考虑年费卡",
      "slide_index": 11
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start": 443.093,
      "end": 446.962,
      "text": "本期数据均来自FCAC和五大银行官网",
      "slide_index": 12
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start": 447.762,
      "end": 449.503,
      "text": "完整链接在屏幕上",
      "slide_index": 13
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start": 450.303,
      "end": 452.831,
      "text": "以上就是本期全部引用来源",
      "slide_index": 14
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start": 453.631,
      "end": 455.981,
      "text": "下期我讲银行存款利息",
      "slide_index": 15
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start": 456.281,
      "end": 459.65,
      "text": "你存在五大银行里的钱，一年能赚多少",
      "slide_index": 15
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start": 459.95,
      "end": 461.149,
      "text": "关注我别错过",
      "slide_index": 15
    }
